I bought a puller for about $15:

http://picasaweb.google.ca/lh/photo/hV5RfpzcOFwC2FcY2E_Zrg

I used this to pull the steering wheel from my 73 bus and it worked great,
except for fiddling with the adjustable arms to get it to fit on the wheel
correctly.
I got mine at Princess Auto, but I'm sure you can find them at many other
places as well.

